{"tid":366307,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台民視：台灣就是台灣，不是中華台北！","createTime":"2017-08-20T02:32:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-20T14:41:42.000Z","uid":23707,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1086c50caf2189f56962b9c742a31914fb12bfdd","tid":366307,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T02:32:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2017-08-19/95372\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2017-08-19%2F95372&d=FJ9giSPoXkpqphHnI1VCHkzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=ee5c88dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2017-08-19/95372</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/20/103215_af9834b4d8f1d5d117931ce2e43bf9a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F20%2F103215_af9834b4d8f1d5d117931ce2e43bf9a4.jpg&h=17b31919&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n備受外界矚目的2017台北世界大學運動會今（19）晚就要舉行開幕典禮，位於新北市林口區的民視總部，距離世大運選手村不遠，今天一早被網友發現高掛起「台灣就是台灣」、「台灣不是中華台北」等中英文布條，引發網友熱議。<br />\n<br />\n世大運籌備至今，不久前才發生過英文版的媒體手冊上，關於「Taiwan（台灣）」的詞彙，都被以「Chinese Taipei（中華台北）」取代，甚至連地理位置介紹的部分也是如此，造成有「Introduction of Our Island-Chinese Taipei !（介紹我們的島嶼─中華台北！）」、「Chinese Taipei is long and narrow（中華台北地形狹長）」等語句發生，引發爭議後，世大運組委會已將部分名詞改回。<br />\n<br />\n有網友上午於PTT爆掛，以「民視爆氣了」為題指出，民視在林口總部高掛布條，強調「台灣就是台灣」、「台灣不是中華台北」等，被網友推爆。不久後，也有網友在臉書社團「林口大家庭 Linkou-Family」張貼民視高掛「Taiwan is not Chinese Taipei（台灣不是中華台北）」、「Let Taiwan be Taiwan（台灣就是台灣）」等布條的照片。"},{"pid":"4733b3d174d6128c831c8f25d524223ca5a8d3bb","tid":366307,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T14:33:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"252667edeab2dc34b24f6a6ec37bfa3f5f12301a","tid":366307,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T14:34:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f29832faadeb9772bcd8dca0aad373bf4f43059","tid":366307,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T14:41:42.000Z","msg":"我係中華台北人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}